Installation:

git clone git://github.com/Oletros/dotvim.git
Create symlinks:

ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc (_vimrc in Windows)
ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc (_gvimrc in Windows)
ln -s ~/.vim/tags/ctags.cnf ~/.ctags (ctags.cnf in Windows)

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

Original: http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/
vimrc: https://github.com/spf13/spf13-vim
